-- Kansas City Royals Sign Free-Agent Outfielder Francoeur to One-Year Deal
-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 2010-12-08T20:52:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-08/kansas-city-royals-sign-free-agent-outfielder-francoeur-to-one-year-deal.html
The Kansas City Royals signed free-
agent outfielder Jeff Francoeur to a one-year contract, the
Major League Baseball team said.  Francoeur, 26, hit a combined .249 with 13 home runs and 65
runs batted in for the New York Mets and Texas Rangers last
season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  